original_title: Ski Canada Presents Warren Miller's Comedy Classics
overview: Warren Millers COMEDY CLASSICS takes some of the funniest moments from the master of movies and puts them together on one tape for the first time. You'll laugh to familiar Miller scenes such as the beginner' rope tow and chair lift, the famous water jump sequences and skiers slipn' sliden' and crashn'.
title: Ski Canada Presents Warren Miller's Comedy Classics
